{"word":"ἄποτος","slug":"ἄποτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄποτος</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not drinkable</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>never drinking</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:— <i>not drinking, without drink</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}